---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const locale = 'en';
const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy';
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} locale={locale} description="Privacy Policy of FabulousArt â€“ Fabienne Meyer, Zurich.">

  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h1 class="legal-page__title">{pageTitle}</h1>
      <p class="legal-page__updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-page__content">

        <h2>1. Controller</h2>
        <p>
          Fabienne Meyer<br />
          FabulousArt<br />
          Zurich, Switzerland<br />
          Email: info.fabulousart@gmail.com
        </p>

        <h2>2. Overview</h2>
        <p>
          Protecting your personal data is very important to me. In this privacy policy, I inform you
          about the personal data I collect, process, and use in connection with my website fabulous-art.ch.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Hosting and Content Delivery</h2>
        <p>
          This website is hosted on <strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong>. When you visit the website,
          technical data such as your IP address, browser type, operating system, referrer URL, and
          time of access are automatically collected by Cloudflare. This is technically necessary to
          deliver the website and ensure its security.
        </p>
        <p>
          Cloudflare may transfer data to the USA. Cloudflare is certified under the EU-US Data
          Privacy Framework. For more information, see
          <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>4. File Uploads (Custom Drawings)</h2>
        <p>
          When you upload reference images through the order form, they are stored in
          <strong>Cloudflare R2</strong>. Uploaded files are used exclusively for processing your
          order and are deleted upon completion. Storage takes place on Cloudflare servers.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Contact Form and Email</h2>
        <p>
          When you use the contact or order form, your information (name, email address, message,
          and any order details) is transmitted to me via <strong>Mailjet</strong>. Processing is
          carried out for the purpose of responding to your inquiry or processing your order.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mailjet stores and processes data on servers within the EU. For more information, see
          <a href="https://www.mailjet.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mailjet's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Google Fonts</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses fonts from <strong>Google Fonts</strong>. When loading the page, your
          browser establishes a connection to Google servers, which transmits your IP address to
          Google. For more information, see
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website does not use its own cookies for tracking or marketing purposes. Technically
          necessary cookies may be set by the hosting provider Cloudflare to ensure the security
          and functionality of the website.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Under the Swiss Data Protection Act (FADP) and, where applicable, the EU General Data
          Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the following rights:
        </p>
        <p>
          Right of access to your stored data, right to rectification of inaccurate data, right to
          deletion of your data, right to restriction of processing, right to data portability, and
          right to object to processing.
        </p>
        <p>
          To exercise your rights, please contact me at: info.fabulousart@gmail.com
        </p>

        <h2>9. Changes</h2>
        <p>
          I reserve the right to amend this privacy policy as needed to adapt it to changed legal
          requirements or changes to my services. The current version on this website always applies.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-4xl));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-5xl);
  }

  .legal-page__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .legal-page__updated {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .legal-page__content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .legal-page__content h2:first-child {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .legal-page__content p {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .legal-page__content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-page__content a {
    color: var(--color-black);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .legal-page__content a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .legal-page__content strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
